The Four Freedoms Guaranteed by the GPL:
=46reedom zero is the freedom to run the program as you wish for any purpos=
e.=20

=46reedom one is the freedom to study the source code and change it
to do what you wish.

=46reedom two is the freedom to help your neighbour, that's the
freedom to make copies and distribute them to others when you
wish.

=46reedom three is the freedom to help your community, that's the
freedom to publish or distribute modified versions when you wish.

